Git for bash


Install this

1) Get this                         :    git clone git://github.com/progman/gitbash.git ~/.config/gitbash.git
2) Add this in your .bashrc line    :    echo "source ~/.config/gitbash.git/gitbash;" >> ~/.bashrc
3) Use this (cd in your git repo)


Update this

1) Go to this repo                  :    cd ~/.config/gitbash.git/
2) Update this repo                 :    git pull
